Cash Out is an upcoming American action film starring John Travolta, Kristin Davis, Lukas Haas, Quavo, and Joel Cohen. It was directed by Ives, and written by Dipo Oseni and Doug Richardson.  The film is scheduled to be released on April 26, 2024.


Cast[edit]
John Travolta as Mason Goddard[1]
Kristin Davis as Amelia Deckard[2]
Quavo as Anton[3]
Lukas Haas as Shawn Goddard [4]
Swen Temmel[4]
Sean Astin[2]
Noel Gugliemi as Hector[2]
Production[edit]
Principal photography occurred in Columbus, Georgia in June 2022.[1][5][6]

Release[edit]
Cash Out is scheduled to be released digital and in limited theaters by Saban Films on April 26, 2024.[7]

Sequel[edit]
A sequel was directed by Randall Emmett. It was filmed in April 2023 and was shot at the Scarlet Pearl Casino Resort in D'Iberville, Mississippi and other locations across the Mississippi Gulf Coast.[8][9]
